How to create servlet using javax.servlet.Servlet interface.
There are 5 methods in Servlet interface .


	1.public abstract void init(javax.servlet.ServletConfig);
	2.public ServletConfig getServletConfigt();
	3.public void service(javax.servlet.ServletRequest,javax.servlet.ServletResponse);
	4.public abstract java.lang.String getServletInfo();
	5.public abstract void destroy();

Life cycle methods 1,3,5.

We will use the method by overriding the methods
mapping -> web.xml (Deployment descriptor)


